DoliProspectFormAnonymousHubUrlTitle = Hub page link (no sales user in token)
DoliProspectFormAnonymousHubUrlHelp = Signed link with no expiry date in the token: no sales user (0); the link stays valid until the public-form secret is changed. Use this to embed the hub in a website (iframe, button, etc.): visitors can enter a Dolibarr consultant e-mail on the page to attach a sales representative when needed. This link targets the current entity (%s).
DoliProspectFormAnonymousHubUrlUnavailable = Cannot build the link: missing or uninitialized public-form secret (re-enable the module or contact your administrator).

