DoliProspectFormSetup = DoliProspectForm setup
Settings = Settings
DoliProspectFormSetupPage = Configure signed public form links, submission and invitation email templates, and substitution keys. On activation, default email templates (public-form third party, invitation, submission notification) are added if missing.
DOLIPROSPECTFORM_TOKEN_VALIDITY_DAYS = Link validity (days)
DOLIPROSPECTFORM_TOKEN_VALIDITY_DAYSTooltip = Number of days after which the link stops being valid, counted from when the token is issued (exp field). For mail sent from Dolibarr, substitution tags are normally recomputed at actual send time, so the period starts at send—not when the third party was created or when a draft was opened earlier. Does not apply to the public « no sales user » link in module setup (token without exp; invalid if the secret is rotated).
DOLIPROSPECTFORM_PUBLIC_DEFAULT_USER = Technical user (public forms)
DOLIPROSPECTFORM_PUBLIC_DEFAULT_USERTooltip = Dolibarr user used for technical operations (third party / contact / file creation) when the token has no valid sales representative. Pick « First active user (automatic) » to keep the default behaviour (first active user of the entity).
DoliProspectFormTechnicalUserAutomatic = First active user (automatic)
DOLIPROSPECTFORM_PUBLIC_FORM_INDIVIDUAL = Public individual form
DOLIPROSPECTFORM_PUBLIC_FORM_INDIVIDUALTooltip = When disabled, the individual public form and the matching choice on the hub page are no longer available.
DOLIPROSPECTFORM_PUBLIC_FORM_PROFESSIONAL = Public business form
DOLIPROSPECTFORM_PUBLIC_FORM_PROFESSIONALTooltip = When disabled, the business public form and the matching choice on the hub page are no longer available.
DOLIPROSPECTFORM_SUBMISSION_NOTIFY_TEMPLATE_ID = Email template for submission notifications
DOLIPROSPECTFORM_SUBMISSION_NOTIFY_TEMPLATE_IDTooltip = User-type template used to notify the assigned sales representative (or the fallback address) after each public form submission. A default template is created when the module is enabled.
DOLIPROSPECTFORM_SUBMISSION_NOTIFY_FALLBACK_EMAIL = Notification email when no sales representative is set
DOLIPROSPECTFORM_SUBMISSION_NOTIFY_FALLBACK_EMAILTooltip = Used when the token has no sales user or the user has no valid email. Initialized with the company main email.
