DoliProspectFormSubstitutionHelpTitle = Email template substitution keys
DoliProspectFormSubstitutionHelpBody = Use these tags in Dolibarr email templates. They are replaced when the message is composed by a logged-in user (that user is the sales representative in the link; when the message is tied to a third party or an object linked to a third party, the third party id is embedded for data update).<br><b>__DOLIPROSPECTFORM_PUBLIC_LINK_HUB__</b>: routing page (individual or business); the token may encode a known sales rep or 0; an optional consultant email on that page can attach a rep when it matches an active Dolibarr user email.<br><b>__DOLIPROSPECTFORM_PUBLIC_LINK_PARTICULIER__</b> or <b>__DOLIPROSPECTFORM_PUBLIC_LINK_INDIVIDUAL__</b>: URL of the individual (household) public form (includes entity and signed token).<br><b>__DOLIPROSPECTFORM_PUBLIC_LINK_PROFESSIONNEL__</b> or <b>__DOLIPROSPECTFORM_PUBLIC_LINK_PROFESSIONAL__</b>: URL of the professional (company) public form (includes entity and signed token).<br><br><b>After a public form submission</b>: <b>__DOLIPROSPECTFORM_SUBMISSION_*__</b> tags (reference, type, date, contact, sales user, SIREN/SIRET/NAF, Dolibarr third-party card URL, etc.) are filled on automatic notification sends; standard <b>__THIRDPARTY_*__</b> and <b>__MYCOMPANY_*__</b> tags remain available when the template is used with the third party as context.
DoliProspectFormPublicThirdpartyNotFound = Third party not found. This link is no longer valid.

